summary: This is just a house I made for my friend, whom is unsure of modding Skyrim, so I kept it simple for him. You can enjoy it too, but it was mostly made for my friend!
descriptionHtml:
Mod for a friend, nothing too special, just the basics and one or two updates, just because I just remembered I forgot to add the Alchemy & Enchanting stations! Oh No!

Well enjoy it and no need to ban this file, due to the fact it is just vanilla game content and nothing else.

Thanks and Peace Out!
author: Pipboy372
